These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, coffee, hot-chocolate, juice
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, motorbike, roller
1. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
3. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the person driving the roller is between the person driving the car and the person driving the motorbike##2
6. the person drinking juice is the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Beverage   | juice | milk     | hot-chocolate | coffee |
| Transport     | bike     | motorbike | roller  | car      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, pink, brown, blue
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, helicopter, snowmobile, trike
1. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person who likes brown is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Color   | ivory | pink    | blue     | brown  |
| Transport     | bus    | snowmobile | helicopter | trike |

