.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
4 different games are played: domino, canasta, snooker, chess
4 different pets are kept: cat, lizard, rabbit, snake
1. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
2. the person playing canasta is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person playing chess##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3
5. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Game   | canasta   | snooker   | domino  | chess |
| Pet           | lizard | snake | rabbit | cat  |

