.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, collecting, dancing, fishing
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, tiparillo, dunhill, davidoff
1. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the dunhill-smoker##2
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
4. the dunhill-smoker is on the left or right of the davidoff-smoker##3
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
6. the prince-smoker is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | collecting | board-games | fishing | dancing  |
| Cigar   | tiparillo  | prince   | davidoff  | dunhill |

