.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, amaryllis, poppy, marigold
1. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person who growsbegonia is on the left or right of the person who growsamaryllis##3
4. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
5. the person who growsmarigold is the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | 7up    | fanta   | hot-chocolate | soy-milk    |
| Flower      | amaryllis | begonia | poppy       | marigold |

