.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, juice, soy-milk
There 4 different types of food: carrot, pear, potato, avocado
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person eating potato is between the person eating avocado and the person drinking juice##2
3. the person eating carrot is between the person eating potato and the person drinking coffee##2
4. the person eating avocado is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | coffee | juice | soy-milk | fanta |
| Food   | pear | carrot  | potato    | avocado  |

