2. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
4. the fan of blues is between the fan of salsa and the fan of punk##2
5. the person driving the ship is the person driving the ship##1
6. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the snowmobile and the fan of punk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | punk | blues | salsa     |
| Transport     | airplane | van  | ship   | snowmobile |

