.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, security-guard, doctor, manager
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, chinese, nigerian, russian
1. the argentine is on the right of the chinese##1
2. the doctor is between the russian and the chinese##2
3. the security-guard is the chinese##1
4. the nigerian is on the left of the chinese##1
5. the manager is on the left or right of the argentine##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| Job   | photographer | security-guard | doctor      | manager   |
| Nationality   | nigerian  | chinese    | argentine | russian |

