.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, chess, filmmaking, writing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, skiing, golf, sailing
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
5. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
6. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby       | card-games | filmmaking | writing    | chess      |
| Sport   | golf       | sailing       | skiing | badminton |

