2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
3. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
4. the bolivar-smoker is on the far left##1
5. the siglo-smoker is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |      3      |   4    |
| Cigar   | bolivar     | blend  | oliveros | siglo |
| Pet     | guinea-pig | turtle | hamster     | rat    |

