.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, milk, soy-milk
House: cottage, modern, palace, townhouse
1. the palace house is on the far right##1
2. the townhouse house is the townhouse house##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3
4. the cottage house is on the far left or far right##3
5. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the palace house##3
6. the cottage house is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the palace house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | fanta     | cola     | milk          | soy-milk |
| House      | cottage | modern | townhouse | palace  |

 